## INSTALLATION / CONFIG

composer create-project symfony/skeleton

mv skeleton/* ./
mv skeleton/.* ./
rmdir skeleton


composer require twig annotations asset form orm validator    
composer require --dev maker profiler debug-bundle fakerphp/faker ormfixtures      
composer require symfony/expression-language  :  Provides an engine that can compile and evaluate expressions


